info-service/racing/dates/2026-04-12/meetings/R/KAL/races/4/form/10?jurisdiction=NSW"}}],"oddsUpdateTime":"2026-04-12T00:34:51.000Z","fixedOddsUpdateTime":"2026-04-11T21:49:13.000Z","raceComments":"{\"comment\":\"6. NISTIRITH capped off some strong form when scoring a well-deserved maiden win over 1100m here last start, putting them away with authority by over a length when taking them all the way. She looks well placed again, and with further improvement to come, she can certainly go on with it. 7. STYLIN' was not disgraced when fifth over 1400m at Pinjarra-Scarpside last time out 7 weeks ago, finishing just under 4 lengths off the winner. He won on debut here near the start of the season, and he is peaking at the right time for his return to his home track. Hard to beat. 3. JAYASHREE resumes after 5 months, and she was competitive at her last run before a break when finishing fifth as the favourite over 1500m at York. Follow any positive market moves. 2. GUARD THE MULLAH showed good early speed here last start and was only claimed late, fading to finish fourth over 1300m. He will be peaking at his third start from the Rod Brown stable, and with the aid of a 2kg claim, he can win this.\",\"runners\":[6,7,3,2],\"exclusive\":true}","ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,7,6,4]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,7,6,2]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[6,7,4,5]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[6,7,2,4]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[6,7,3,9]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,7,6,4]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[6,7,2,3]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"KAL","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"KAL","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"KAL","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"E